# Tell GitHub Linguist what to count (and what to ignore)

# Ignore documentation and frontend files
*.md linguist-documentation=true
*.json linguist-documentation=true
*.js linguist-documentation=true
*.jsx linguist-documentation=true
*.html linguist-documentation=true
*.css linguist-documentation=true

# Explicitly mark Arduino and C++ files as source
*.ino linguist-language=C++
*.cpp linguist-language=C++
*.h linguist-language=C
*.c linguist-language=C

Fix language detection: prioritise C++ and ignore docs
